Resource Profile: DDCC:VS DocumentSigned

Defining URL:http://worldhealthorganization.github.io/ddcc/StructureDefinition/DDCCVSDocumentSigned
Version:0.3.1
Name:DDCCVSDocumentSigned
Title:DDCC:VS DocumentSigned
Status:Active as of 1/25/22, 2:32 PM
Definition:

A DDCC:VS Document Signed is a document bundle containing the DDCC:VS that has a digital signature.

Publisher:WHO
Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://worldhealthorganization.github.io/ddcc/StructureDefinition/DDCCVSDocumentSigned
